I kept wearing it most of my life, except it got 
too... Then I transferred it to the right, and then

26:03.917 --> 26:11.265
I finally... got too large and it kept falling off 
and I quit wearing it as a result of that. Because

26:17.775 --> 26:22.827
I'm thinking that that's also one of those Aggie 
unifying features. That is a graduate unifying.

26:27.057 --> 26:27.839
There's no question about it. The ring is the one 
that And even today, with men and women, with a very

26:30.010 --> 26:43.710
small percentage of the student body being in the 
core, that ring is still the common unifying

26:30.010 --> 26:43.710
factor.

