Curiously, I'd have it in the room. I'd put it on at 
night when everybody was around. Take it off.

26:56.989 --> 26:58.311
Because I didn't dare wear it. The seniors would 
object. What are the qualities of being an Aggie?

27:07.788 --> 27:19.718
I think the quality of being an Aggie is

27:07.788 --> 27:19.718
a good deal of self-confidence.

27:23.321 --> 27:26.084
That somehow, I'm all right. What I do is okay.

27:31.756 --> 27:32.517
It lives with me. I had no trouble with courses. I 
had no trouble with studies. I felt I could do

27:39.347 --> 27:44.154
anything except be a military leader or be 
elected.

27:48.059 --> 27:51.664
And I think that's partly my personality that I 
had.

27:54.508 --> 27:58.274
I was sort of a squeaky voice fellow. I didn't gain 
my loud voice until I got into the military itself,

28:02.080 --> 28:09.111
and had to, and somebody said, sound

28:02.080 --> 28:09.111
off.

28:12.356 --> 28:26.519
There was also a,

28:12.356 --> 28:26.519
probably a kind of arrogance, too,

28:12.356 --> 28:26.519
that it was better. You're saying... Yeah, you're 
saying that it's more than just confidence.

28:36.540 --> 28:37.001
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

28:41.108 --> 28:42.550
Mm-hmm.

28:50.963 --> 28:56.792
Mm-hmm.

29:01.075 --> 29:07.882
And they were confident that your education was

29:01.075 --> 29:07.882
first class. Now, you must have known when you 
came, you must have known a few Aggie graduates.

29:15.129 --> 29:15.409
Yes. Do you now realize that you saw that kind of 
quality in them too, some of those qualities? Yes,

29:25.679 --> 29:26.340
I think so. That's the reason why I guess I came to 
A&M. is that I came across those people

29:29.830 --> 29:43.950
that

29:29.830 --> 29:43.950
carried on that kind of confidence, knew them.

29:47.575 --> 29:52.122
And you never thought about going anywhere else, 
transferring? I did earlier, yes. No, no, I mean

29:53.163 --> 29:54.926
once you enrolled here. Once enrolled? Oh, no. No, 
I was most disappointed. Joe Cole, who left the

29:59.699 --> 30:07.186
early part of us here and went to Texas Tech, I 
couldn't see. I just said, you're going for an

